{"tid":1175344,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 架車著engine燈code P0171","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T10:41:01.000Z","uid":39069,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce6a8e65974812f5358ade242af80cdc658694f","tid":1175344,"uid":39069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"小弟架車係Audi A4 Avant 2.0T 2009年既multitronic版本<br />\n其實都揸落無分別，但始終著燈搵左車房跟<br />\n前後3個星期換左空氣流量計、火咀x4、圖片果塊野都係照著返燈<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQPSfZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQPSfZR.jpg&h=485b99bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都洗左幾千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬窮撚一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請教下連登高手睇下知唔知邊到出問題會著P0171 code"},{"pid":"5142a05f332fb73216fac6caecab926714dd2673","tid":1175344,"uid":24995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.obd-codes.com/p0171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.obd-codes.com%2Fp0171&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2DUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=77d713c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.obd-codes.com/p0171</a>"},{"pid":"61493ce9dbb04ab0481cfe42860325cdbd4c070b","tid":1175344,"uid":141551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:49:43.000Z","msg":"上網搵下有幾難"},{"pid":"9a136c7bc03b6d4df81c090519d56af053248164","tid":1175344,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:51:37.000Z","msg":"自己升級咗做稀薄燃燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27696b7175788bfe0c9d50e511e18f8e1719fe6","tid":1175344,"uid":39069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61493ce9dbb04ab0481cfe42860325cdbd4c070b","tid":1175344,"uid":141551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:49:43.000Z","msg":"上網搵下有幾難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"巴打我上網有搵<br />\n而且都有比車房跟<br />\n<br />\n上星期換埋o2 sensor都係著燈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次睇下進氣密封有無問題<br />\n<br />\n都想問下有無巴打有相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3ca098675ada4ae7d7d1a2fd628301c4c33dc4","tid":1175344,"uid":204915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"之前我部AUDI A6 都係著ENGINE 燈，整來整去都會著，因為我好小揸，所以都無理佢由佢著，有時入啲靚油又會熄燈之後又著返。"},{"pid":"1288f9daa5f036f8f468370294c4c454a2478afe","tid":1175344,"uid":39069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3ca098675ada4ae7d7d1a2fd628301c4c33dc4","tid":1175344,"uid":204915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"之前我部AUDI A6 都係著ENGINE 燈，整來整去都會著，因為我好小揸，所以都無理佢由佢著，有時入啲靚油又會熄燈之後又著返。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個code好難跟 車房斷估叫我換零件<br />\n照行得走得 真係唔想跟 我都好小揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364f1962c1b98f927f45ce6ecae25eebf123f26a","tid":1175344,"uid":118492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"小弟部gti 都遇過呢個問題，前前後後換左2次空氣流量計，頭一次換左就係彈簧/重量唔岩所以照著，之後車房唔收錢幫我整多次搞掂"},{"pid":"1b07e83bd75c9f89aa2a43e03af2c05fd53a1beb","tid":1175344,"uid":39069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"364f1962c1b98f927f45ce6ecae25eebf123f26a","tid":1175344,"uid":118492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"小弟部gti 都遇過呢個問題，前前後後換左2次空氣流量計，頭一次換左就係彈簧/重量唔岩所以照著，之後車房唔收錢幫我整多次搞掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打分享經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都換左空氣流量計，要再check下件野有無出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca77e5a4e6446e7b6df8192956774f0e5a123f1","tid":1175344,"uid":13416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor